{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-lecture-template-tsx","path":"/lecture/운영체제/2023-02-28-Virtual-Memory-관리-2/","result":{"data":{"allMarkdownRemark":{"edges":[{"node":{"html":"<h2 id=\"software-components\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#software-components\" aria-label=\"software components permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📌software components</h2>\n<h3 id=\"allocation-strategies\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#allocation-strategies\" aria-label=\"allocation strategies permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📖allocation strategies</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>각 프로세스에게 메모리를 얼마 만큼 줄 것인가?\n<ul>\n<li>고정 할당 : 프로세스 실행 동안 고정된 크기 메모리 할당</li>\n<li>가변 할당 : 프로세스 실행 동안 할당하는 메로리 크기가 유동적</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>고려 사항\n<ul>\n<li>너무 큰 메모리 할당 -> 메모리 낭비</li>\n<li>너무 적은 메모리 할당 -> page fault rate 상승</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"fetch-strategies\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#fetch-strategies\" aria-label=\"fetch strategies permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📖fetch strategies</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>특정 page를 메모리에 언제 적재할 것인가?\n<ul>\n<li>demand fetch : 필요할때 적재한다, 프로세스가 참조하는 페이지만 적재</li>\n<li>anticipatory fetch(pre-paging) : 참조될 가능성 높은 page 예측 및 미리 적재</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"placement-strategies\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#placement-strategies\" aria-label=\"placement strategies permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📖placement strategies</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>page/segment를 어디에 적재할 것 인가?</li>\n<li>paging system에서는 불필요 -> 모두 크기가 같음 어디를 놓아도 똑같다</li>\n<li>first fit, best fit, worst fit, next fit등이 있음</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"replacement-strategies\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#replacement-strategies\" aria-label=\"replacement strategies permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📖replacement strategies</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>새로운 page를 어떤 page와 교체 할 것인가?(비어있는 page frame이 없는 경우)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"cleaning-strategies\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#cleaning-strategies\" aria-label=\"cleaning strategies permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📖cleaning strategies</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>변경된 page를 언제 write-back할 것인가?</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>main memory에서 변경된 내용을 swap-device에 반영하는걸 언제 할건지</p>\n<ul>\n<li>demand cleaning : 해당 page가 메모리에서 내려올때</li>\n<li>anticipatory cleaning(pre-cleaning) : 더 이상 변경될 가능성이 없다고 판단되면 미리 write-back</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"load-control-strategies\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#load-control-strategies\" aria-label=\"load control strategies permalink\" class=\"anchor-header before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>📖load control strategies</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>시스템의 multi-programming degree 조절</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>얼마나 많은 프로세스를 동시에 수행될 것 인가</p>\n<ul>\n<li>plateau(고원) 영역 유지(적당히 유지)해야함</li>\n<li>under load : 저부하 상태, 시스템 자원 낭비</li>\n<li>over load : 고부하 상태, 자원 경쟁 심화, thrashing 발생\n<ul>\n<li>thrashing(스레싱) 발생 : 과도한 page fault가 발생하는 현상</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#software-components\">📌software components</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#allocation-strategies\">📖allocation strategies</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#fetch-strategies\">📖fetch strategies</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#placement-strategies\">📖placement strategies</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#replacement-strategies\">📖replacement strategies</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#cleaning-strategies\">📖cleaning strategies</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#load-control-strategies\">📖load control strategies</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"Virtual Memory 관리 2","date":"2023년 02월 27일","tags":["CS"]}}}]}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/lecture/운영체제/2023-02-28-Virtual-Memory-관리-2/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/lecture/운영체제/2023-02-27-Virtual-Memory-4/"},"frontmatter":{"categories":["운영체제"],"title":"Virtual Memory 1","date":"2023-02-27 01:00:00 +0900","tags":["CS"]}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/lecture/운영체제/2023-02-28-Virtual-Memory-관리-1/"},"frontmatter":{"categories":["운영체제"],"title":"Virtual Memory 관리 1","date":"2023-02-28 01:00:00 +0900","tags":["CS"]}}}},"staticQueryHashes":[],"slicesMap":{}}